{"tid":132722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐申請司法覆核「我爸是梁特」機管局報告","createTime":"2017-02-24T04:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T06:20:54.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ece6edb06c686a73c9eebdbc3f984c0cf8496a93","tid":132722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T04:54:51.000Z","msg":"特首梁振英遭踢爆疑於去年3月向機場員工施壓，令幼女梁頌昕獲特事特辦享特權，由國泰職員代送行李入禁區。機管局及後提交報告指代送行李沒違保安程序，由於梁頌昕行李不需覆檢，故毋須同行同檢。港龍航空公司空姐就機管局報告結果向法庭申請司法覆核，法庭今聽罷陳詞後批出申請許可，案件將排期聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據香港法例494章《航空保安條例》擬訂的《香港航空保安計劃》，其中第6.2.10段列明旅客及其手提行李須同時接受保安檢查，申請人認為任何旅客與其手提行李必須同行同檢，包括首檢（X光檢查）及覆檢（人手搜查），並非僅針對後者。"},{"pid":"cd33cd186b6a4da595c7a9bbae56ad878236939b","tid":132722,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1df48a10ba97916143c3dcf26e67a55fd08e639","tid":132722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:11:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170224&amp;guid=56346906&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170224%26guid%3D56346906%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQsozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=19fc29c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170224%26guid%3D56346906%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=f303b456\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170224&amp;guid=56346906&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"86f8fa4a765c9d0c80d34bcd6e013019277078b7","tid":132722,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:14:01.000Z","msg":"等睇空姐秘密影片流出<br />\n（689一定搵辦法攪佢）"},{"pid":"b011a588a151e2c78594ad93a46f88685688fb18","tid":132722,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354ae216700447aca47fb4376ce571c10b2817db","tid":132722,"uid":51436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"我諗9成香港人已經忘記左件事"}]}